Uses of Package
generalRepository

  • Packages that use generalRepository 
    Package Description
    assaultParty
    This package contains the AssaultParty Monitor and all other interfaces to the entities to access to the methods, for example, IMasterThief is the Master Thief interface of the AssaultParty Instance.
    controlAndCollectionSite
    This package contains the ControlAndCollectioSite Monitor and all other interfaces to the entities to acess to the methods, for example, IMasterThief is the Master Thief interface of the ControlAndCollectioSite Instance.
    generalRepository
    General Repository package, it is the log that will be the gateway to all the information of the heist, it will be responsible for printing in a file the log information of the heist.
    main
    Main package, it contains the constants file and the definition of the entities: Master Thief and Ordinary Thief.
    museum
    This package contains the Museum Monitor, Room class and all other interfaces to the entities to access to the methods, for example, IMasterThief is the Master Thief interface of the Museum Instance.
